TypeDefinition

createHashmapObject ["XPS_AP_typ_Method"]
Authors

Crashdome

Description

A Method is a collection used in Heirarchical Task Networks which decompose into smaller subtasks based on a satisfied condition. These collections are usually found in a XPS_AP_typ_CompoundTask in order of priority.
